{"tid":1854,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"哲學入門書單 各位對哲學有興趣嘅巴打可以睇下","createTime":"2016-11-25T17:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T09:41:58.000Z","uid":12140,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c4e7d2cd9109d7d22cb6773b5b45b822df9b805e","tid":1854,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:17:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最基礎</span>：<br />\nAn introduction to philosophical analysis 4th edition-<strong>John Hospers</strong><br />\nWhat does it all mean?-<strong>Thomas Nagel</strong><br />\nThink: a compelling introduction to philosophy-<strong>Simon Blackburn</strong><br />\nThe Philosophers Habitat - <strong>Laurence Goldstein</strong><br />\nPhilosophy:The Pursuit of Wisdom-<strong>Louis Pojman</strong><br />\nMetaphysics: Riddle of existence -<strong>Conee and Sider</strong><br />\nDoing Philosophy: An Introduction Through Thought Experiments-<strong>Lewis Vaughn and Theodore Schick</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">以下係就住各topic嘅推薦入門書</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Philosophy of religion</span>: The Miracle of Theism Argument for and against the existence of God-<strong>J.L. Mackie</strong> <br />\nIs There a God- <strong>Richard Swinburne</strong> <br />\nThe God Delusion-<strong>Richard Dawkins</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Logic</span>: A concise introduction to Logic<br />\nThe Logic Book<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Philosophy of Mind</span>:<br />\nPhilosophy of Mind- <strong>Jaegwon Kim</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Ethics</span> : The element of moral philosophy-<strong>James Rachels</strong><br />\nHow are we to live-<strong>Peter Singer</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Epistemology</span><br />\nEpistemology -<strong>Richard Feldman</strong><br />\nAn Introduction to Contemporary Epistemology -<strong>Jonathan Dancy</strong><br />\n其實值得睇嘅入門書仲有好多，但係未能盡錄，歡迎大家補充"},{"pid":"d24150dfdb86de095bb2176ab088b0f90d9fb067","tid":1854,"uid":798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:20:22.000Z","msg":"有無中文"},{"pid":"82f72a1c5e1687c66994163163224a8b1745be55","tid":1854,"uid":349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:45:09.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n利申：哲學系"},{"pid":"544d0fea0cef4ae6c46277aeb739266d8caa0d77","tid":1854,"uid":1412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T18:19:06.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e70cba9fb2067b7c1cbac521662977e1f4d5b76e","tid":1854,"uid":2438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T00:31:13.000Z","msg":"Sider果本應該放去metaphysics入門啦<br />\n<br />\n其實入門書唔洗睇咁多，一本清楚既就夠。上面有啲書好差，好唔清楚，好舊。<br />\n<br />\n我建議睇：what does it all mean，一本就夠"},{"pid":"f17464afcf56baef81f263869bd355881166efa3","tid":1854,"uid":2438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T00:32:12.000Z","msg":"利申 哲學graduate student"},{"pid":"8be8dd80ac53b7c61476c22661cb289af13b6e93","tid":1854,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T01:43:08.000Z","msg":"小弟一開始就睇尼采晚期果兩本， 覺得好似開錯左個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\nBtw 多謝介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db553fe09ed75210eb36c170e4a40f271d536681","tid":1854,"uid":10171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T01:50:37.000Z","msg":"睇唔明tractatus,有冇方法搞到睇得明"},{"pid":"53b6002fb38f1321acda22a63c1bfcd3a15e24fd","tid":1854,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:21:15.000Z","msg":"你唔覺得對初學者黎講太深？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係從未接觸過哲學，由零開始既巴絲，<br />\n我推薦呢兩本<br />\nNigel Warburton - A Little History of Philosophy<br />\n絕對係我見過最淺白既哲學書，由Aristotle講到Rawls都有，差不多覆蓋曬所有最出名既哲學家，但好薄好快睇完<br />\n<br />\nMichael Sandel - Justice<br />\n都唔使多講，政治哲學最淺白既入門書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係走生動有趣路線"},{"pid":"1b87dcc388c45dfa09e5beaba63f9e677641bc55","tid":1854,"uid":1098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:35:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<br />\n利申：哲學系</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nme too<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6dbf00acec497ff274e50b8348c41078eaac3b9","tid":1854,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無中文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國哲學史 勞思光先生著<br />\n獨創基源問題研究法 有全面性判斷 <br />\n算係一本最清晰既中國哲學史"},{"pid":"74f92dc45ee7f9da2adb37ae13c221bfd6e58db2","tid":1854,"uid":20663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T04:55:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇唔明tractatus,有冇方法搞到睇得明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇 M.O Mounce 本introduction<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ead7c4fd35212e98874021b1c797c7a401ca97e","tid":1854,"uid":12140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sider果本應該放去metaphysics入門啦<br />\n<br />\n其實入門書唔洗睇咁多，一本清楚既就夠。上面有啲書好差，好唔清楚，好舊。<br />\n<br />\n我建議睇：what does it all mean，一本就夠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實嗰本我係打算擺去metaphysics <br />\n只係唔記得打<br />\n至於入門書唔使睇咁多？<br />\n我仲記得自己undergrad時major科科A range，但係啲professor 畀我嘅意見都係undergrad要睇多啲入門書，唔好掛住睇journal<br />\n入門書其實嗰種寫法先係適合初學者慢慢細讀，嗰種推論方法係最值得學"},{"pid":"9fc84385c416e185ac2eb0a8fdfa0b30f29c616a","tid":1854,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:19:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇唔明tractatus,有冇方法搞到睇得明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n初學就唔好睇tractatus啦"},{"pid":"3a8724e57b363d472ea038d9a9b47b649c366850","tid":1854,"uid":5283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T06:27:46.000Z","msg":"我既入門書只係蘇菲的世界 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb397e5e3da5c35012f73cb05be922db7efe0da","tid":1854,"uid":6685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T06:55:54.000Z","msg":"咁快有高質post<br />\nLm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f12ab3b38cc1e005c0531d35b98bbca346d733f","tid":1854,"uid":349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T07:40:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我既入門書只係蘇菲的世界 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜我太遲接觸呢本書，應該中學就開始睇"},{"pid":"d925ddf4bf5883a8eef1a3ca8f8d41568fa62463","tid":1854,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:34:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無中文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國哲學史 勞思光先生著<br />\n獨創基源問題研究法 有全面性判斷 <br />\n算係一本最清晰既中國哲學史</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以睇埋<br />\n王邦雄 中國思想史<br />\n台灣學者覺得勞思光寫得唔夠好<br />\n所以後來集結好多人再寫嘅本"},{"pid":"fde95f43b004178f6c84945a8d6d8cfe913bf21e","tid":1854,"uid":6685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T09:43:50.000Z","msg":"有無啲書講死亡？"},{"pid":"8e5b0abecc13afc9ec28c5caa5a783a882e6ca34","tid":1854,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:04:55.000Z","msg":"政治哲學入門除左sandel同kymlicka之外<br />\njonathan wolff既an introduction to political philosophy同adam swift既political philosophy都係好既入門書"},{"pid":"6f1ceabdf04cc090b9d8774f72459c3bd85fa9c5","tid":1854,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:06:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無啲書講死亡？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nscheffler有本書叫death and the afterlife<br />\n唔知岩唔岩你心水<br />\n佢用一個hypothetical case去講我地點睇the value of life<br />\n幾有意思"},{"pid":"e66d4e8d3786735404b02b4a00b60914db342c6c","tid":1854,"uid":18438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:38:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政治哲學入門除左sandel同kymlicka之外<br />\njonathan wolff既an introduction to political philosophy同adam swift既political philosophy都