"msg":"<blockquote>你唔覺得對初學者黎講太深？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係從未接觸過哲學，由零開始既巴絲，<br />\n我推薦呢兩本<br />\nNigel Warburton - A Little History of Philosophy<br />\n絕對係我見過最淺白既哲學書，由Aristotle講到Rawls都有，差不多覆蓋曬所有最出名既哲學家，但好薄好快睇完<br />\n<br />\nMichael Sandel - Justice<br />\n都唔使多講，政治哲學最淺白既入門書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係走生動有趣路線</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實一啲都唔深<br />\n基本上yr1都會睇呢啲書<br />\n入門書講究四個字，深入淺出<br />\nJustice應該做到呢點<br />\n但係第一本應該係所謂哲普"},{"pid":"ea2a1ebff920a077de7ecd04bb5fb60029e7cd45","tid":1854,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T12:51:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>政治哲學入門除左sandel同kymlicka之外<br />\njonathan wolff既an introduction to political philosophy同adam swift既political philosophy都係好既入門書</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇緊Jonathan Wolff <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港d大學政哲intro 好似基本上都係睇Wolff</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwolff夠簡單 而且cover唔同課題<br />\n仲要有翻譯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWolff好野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3807d203c772b01785fc308dc548dfd4d05113c9","tid":1854,"uid":1644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T12:52:52.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b02b5c6154be839822ae64324a0898f42fefbfc","tid":1854,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9694ad0067506cf100e345bc02e26f2fb849a48","tid":1854,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"lm 多謝分享"},{"pid":"1ecad9642f293036ef305c7b02272277953366c5","tid":1854,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:37:03.000Z","msg":"我剩係對存在主義有興趣<br />\n點睇李天命個本做入門"},{"pid":"24eada16f4dce1be44e29ef53c225308b54fb50b","tid":1854,"uid":29275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:01:05.000Z","msg":"今個sem因為一個course而接觸接觸倫理哲學<br />\n有冇巴打讀過Immanuel Kant<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲深唔太明"},{"pid":"63e390167c142bbc939595b7909098ed9202b1a5","tid":1854,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今個sem因為一個course而接觸接觸倫理哲學<br />\n有冇巴打讀過Immanuel Kant<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲深唔太明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n建議開頭睇淺啲嘅，對哲學多啲認識<br />\nBtw睇康德嘅我都有入門書一本推薦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Immanuel-Kant-Suny-Ethical-Theory/dp/0791420949\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FImmanuel-Kant-Suny-Ethical-Theory%2Fdp%2F0791420949&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMcW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=fa39e9fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Immanuel-Kant-Suny-Ethical-Theory/dp/0791420949</a>"},{"pid":"9fdda1f4e2b008026ac9b4ecf070b63c6b391661","tid":1854,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:38:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我剩係對存在主義有興趣<br />\n點睇李天命個本做入門</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n李天命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔建議<br />\n另外存在主義我冇掂開，所以唔知有咩書可以推薦<br />\n不過如果係尼采就要小心，佢講嘢有時會自己打返自己"},{"pid":"8b34429c252b5f458907c5d9cfc762fad8eb2563","tid":1854,"uid":8569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:42:04.000Z","msg":"做哲撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096a8140a6aa3bc28de5e56f9b1c926ae2173132","tid":1854,"uid":10034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:17:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我剩係對存在主義有興趣<br />\n點睇李天命個本做入門</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n李天命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔建議<br />\n另外存在主義我冇掂開，所以唔知有咩書可以推薦<br />\n不過如果係尼采就要小心，佢講嘢有時會自己打返自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解嘅？我睇左佢本存在主義概論覺得幾易明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔推介嘅原因係因為內容有錯？"},{"pid":"3be417d47aedf74f1d814b9be5da49b3558eabe9","tid":1854,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我剩係對存在主義有興趣<br />\n點睇李天命個本做入門</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n李天命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔建議<br />\n另外存在主義我冇掂開，所以唔知有咩書可以推薦<br />\n不過如果係尼采就要小心，佢講嘢有時會自己打返自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解嘅？我睇左佢本存在主義概論覺得幾易明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔推介嘅原因係因為內容有錯？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一條分析哲撚可以講存在主義講得幾啱，呢點我抱有疑問<br />\n不過我冇睇過本書<br />\n但係易明唔等如啱<br />\n同埋我印象中佢講過歐陸得尼采值得睇，咁你就知佢有幾熟存在主義啦⋯⋯<br />\nBtw佢其實冇香港人想像中咁厲害<br />\n睇多啲哲學書就知佢點解唔叫自己做哲學家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三流哲學家，一流哲道行者"},{"pid":"bd24098b6b7efb764ae14ac4c01330f4462c84be","tid":1854,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:46:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我剩係對存在主義有興趣<br />\n點睇李天命個本做入門</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n李天命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔建議<br />\n另外存在主義我冇掂開，所以唔知有咩書可以推薦<br />\n不過如果係尼采就要小心，佢講嘢有時會自己打返自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解嘅？我睇左佢本存在主義概論覺得幾易明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔推介嘅原因係因為內容有錯？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一條分析哲撚可以講存在主義講得幾啱，呢點我抱有疑問<br />\n不過我冇睇過本書<br />\n但係易明唔等如啱<br />\n同埋我印象中佢講過歐陸得尼采值得睇，咁你就知佢有幾熟存在主義啦⋯⋯<br />\nBtw佢其實冇香港人想像中咁厲害<br />\n睇多啲哲學書就知佢點解唔叫自己做哲學家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三流哲學家，一流哲道行者</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85bf914b52649d988a90cfb822ed525730d131b","tid":1854,"uid":8725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:09:31.000Z","msg":"哲學系畢業有乜工做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846e99d2b83ab21a6262caaf078582388d92a2cd","tid":1854,"uid":2197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:15:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無中文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國哲學史 勞思光先生著<br />\n獨創基源問題研究法 有全面性判斷 <br />\n算係一本最清晰既中國哲學史</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好睇 推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afef8e184d634268d65572e73d70414acb358b6f","tid":1854,"uid":18873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無中文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國哲學史 勞思光先生著<br />\n獨創基源問題研究法 有全面性判斷 <br />\n算係一本最清晰既中國哲學史</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好睇 推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我去台灣讀書學校攞左呢本做課本 大家覺得呢本有點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6322048832c79dfa21a3e23ca51c181e985ef1","tid":1854,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:19:43.000Z","msg":"想了解Locke 同唔同人係natural law 同social contract theory 上嘅睇法 有咩介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e10c246b7dce035bb54d96a7c7c173d8f10c64","tid":1854,"uid":11970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我既入門書只係蘇菲的世界 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中學用左幾年睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b283b6a634734a513befb2c7af08a66bc5260cc","tid":1854,"uid":29275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:30:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今個sem因為一個course而接觸接觸倫理哲學<br />\n有冇巴打讀過Immanuel Kant<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲深唔太明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n建議開頭睇淺啲嘅，對哲學多啲認識<br />\nBtw睇康德嘅我都有入門書一本推薦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Immanuel-Kant-Suny-Ethical-Theory/dp/0791420949\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FImmanuel-Kant-Suny-Ethical-Theory%2Fdp%2F0791420949&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMcW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=fa39e9fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Immanuel-Kant-Suny-Ethical-Theory/dp/0791420949</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n課程教緊metaphysics of moral <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好有趣，但本書既英文好古式，加上概念又難，中譯本又1999<br />\n睇一頁要半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa1de96ddc9239f026c79d6c023898df8991b4b","tid":1854,"uid":22826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"好post留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d94e0292575cd4ef00ac58f7f99b49cfed8bd7","tid":1854,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:15:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想了解Locke 同唔同人係natural law 同social contract theory 上嘅睇法 有咩介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJohn Dunn<br />\nA.J.Simmons<br />\nSimmons講Lockean theory of legitimacy好睇<br />\n如果想睇Hobbes同Locke既比較就睇Macpherson既The Political Theory of Possessive Individualism: Hobbes to Locke 都係經典"},{"pid":"444c8c970c05ac6ae074f3dae76860d1d3a7005b","tid":1854,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:11:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想了解Locke 同唔同人係natural law 同social contract theory 上嘅睇法 有咩介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJohn Dunn<br />\nA.J.Simmons<br />\nSimmons講Lockean theory of legitimacy好睇<br />\n如果想睇Hobbes同Locke既比較就睇Macpherson既The Political Theory of Possessive Individualism: Hobbes to Locke 都係經典</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c6d2f7eff89ecd5eda268eea40926b074d1d16","tid":1854,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T18:00:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無中文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國哲學史 勞思光先生著<br />\n獨創基源問題研究法 有全面性判斷 <br />\n算係一本最清晰既中國哲學史</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好睇 推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我去台灣讀書學校攞左呢本做課本 大家覺得呢本有點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一流，講得好清楚，一句廢話都無，全面性判斷。<br />\n有三本，後兩本較多主觀意見，建議只睇頭一本就夠。"},{"pid":"adc82d9fa12f8831ab38c223d8e18d4a5aa96c26","tid":1854,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:20:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>今個sem因為一個course而接觸接觸倫理哲學<br />\n有冇巴打讀過Immanuel Kant<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲深唔太明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n建議開頭睇淺啲嘅，對哲學多啲認識<br />\nBtw睇康德嘅我都有入門書一本推薦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Immanuel-Kant-Suny-Ethical-Theory/dp/0791420949\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FImmanuel-Kant-Suny-Ethical-Theory%2Fdp%2F0791420949&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMcW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=fa39e9fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Immanuel-Kant-Suny-Ethical-Theory/dp/0791420949</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n課程教緊metaphysics of moral <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好有趣，但本書既英文好古式，加上概念又難，中譯本又1999<br />\n睇一頁要半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好睇中文<br />\n英文仲易明"},{"pid":"613dd6c822cbf7f7e10b898def635e2afbe879e8","tid":1854,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:22:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哲學系畢業有乜工做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認真，其實哲學擺明係有錢人、精英讀嘅科嚟<br />\n如果你諗要搵工，真係唔好讀哲學<br />\n好多哲學大師都係唔同意義上嘅奴隸主嚟"},{"pid":"6f334930b3c847a2e9c2aebf165c281dc071d785","tid":1854,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:22:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無啲書講死亡？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你上youtube<br />\nYale有個course 叫philosophy of death都幾正"},{"pid":"7aca223376db2ab535e76aaefb1a08c24383afb7","tid":1854,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:23:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我既入門書只係蘇菲的世界 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我冇睇過<br />\n到我知有呢本書時，已經唔係我程度需要睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c87447047c62a59e20711f2113b4847c34e0ec","tid":1854,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"推post <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468d90ab13ade3c511d9dbbf91547d669d193753","tid":1854,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595faacb7bc73b178af81b903b638f7030713711","tid":1854,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:03:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17e217acfcaa620534fcc73333e51a677fe17abf","tid":1854,"uid":25869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822f4766e490cd8cafdb3b2bf14dc07f45372024","tid":1854,"uid":29275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:41:46.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇睇Eichmann in Jerusalem <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個本好易明哈哈"},{"pid":"f6ee6f6575ea60bf9a033a6f47683ccc7ceaac0d","tid":1854,"uid":34989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:54:30.000Z","msg":"好奇一問 life, death and meaning: key philosophical readings on the big questions<br />\n大家對佢嘅難度，值唔值得睇等等點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568cd1a9a871c12c1987580ed307ec1497459136","tid":1854,"uid":33625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"de568297e8b63c90877622c682793650d4e4b1bd","tid":1854,"uid":18265