6-11-29T04:17:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無老牟本中國哲學19講??</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你覺得嗰本係入門書咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無理由一開波睇會通中西哲學十四講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e3208426c5061badcc9dd8c897fe671846d324","tid":1854,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:52:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無老牟本中國哲學19講??</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你覺得嗰本係入門書咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無理由一開波睇會通中西哲學十四講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我買咗返嚟冇睇過<br />\n同埋一定唔係入門<br />\n入面講嘅係佢自己對中國哲學嘅見解<br />\n以我所知，入面佢對四端同老子嘅見解已經同其他人有分歧<br />\n一本好嘅入門書應該唔同理論嘅比重都差唔多"},{"pid":"5e7a6c7417dd1f5ebefff1777ac1ef22bf5cffcc","tid":1854,"uid":34300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;無老牟本中國哲學19講??</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你覺得嗰本係入門書咩&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n算係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無理由一開波睇會通中西哲學十四講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n我買咗返嚟冇睇過<br />\n同埋一定唔係入門<br />\n入面講嘅係佢自己對中國哲學嘅見解<br />\n以我所知，入面佢對四端同老子嘅見解已經同其他人有分歧<br />\n一本好嘅入門書應該唔同理論嘅比重都差唔多</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢果堆野都係借人口講佢既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1fe7031328c57370d6d462f9013e36b7e91099","tid":1854,"uid":35927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:11:30.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"021263aa015a6b89b97599a4f5b38eaa170a6021","tid":1854,"uid":43096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:58:15.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d4de96ea6d7d29c290cae2c21924322dae530d10","tid":1854,"uid":7551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:36:08.000Z","msg":"巴打係唔係'Wittgenstein'<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c5feef41a145ebf7d28c06a948490dcc3ddeca","tid":1854,"uid":47028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:45:24.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e99c582ba3d77ff72804b4ea13f068e11cfb9d96","tid":1854,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:52:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無中文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國哲學史 勞思光先生著<br />\n獨創基源問題研究法 有全面性判斷 <br />\n算係一本最清晰既中國哲學史</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以睇埋<br />\n王邦雄 中國思想史<br />\n台灣學者覺得勞思光寫得唔夠好<br />\n所以後來集結好多人再寫嘅本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老實勞思光啲中文唔知點咁<br />\n同某些觀點覺得係同其他老一輩一樣偏幫中國/護短"},{"pid":"242720cdea2f0d2a5bd4c02cbe54a24dfbe38731","tid":1854,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>God delusion, the atheists bible<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n前者真係鞭到啪啪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eaf386c404045ab4b8a8c95b14e44ac3f7a86c6","tid":1854,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"建議睇少少心理學/大腦既書<br />\n<br />\n好多所謂講人性，mind and body,脫離左科學就變左9up<br />\n<br />\n推介how the mind work by Steven pinker"}]}